### Get Assignments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assignments?page=0&size=10

###

### Create Assignment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assignments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": 1,
  "assetId": 1,
  "assignedDate": "2026-07-04",
  "note": "Primary development laptop"
}

###

### Return Asset
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assignments/1/return